    • checkCollideWithGhost

      protected boolean checkCollideWithGhost(Ghost gst)
      Introduce collision target recording to prevent possible respawn point overlap (although it did not happen in the given CSV) and immediate redeath after respawn, which may cause repeated deduction of life in a single collision. Typical scenario: Walking towards the pink ghost in opposite directions at the midpoint of the bottom line.
      Overrides:
      checkCollideWithGhost in class Player_L0
      Parameters:
      gst - the ghost being checked for collision
      Returns:
      T for Collide, F for not
